WEBVTT

01:32.680 --> 01:35.009
[How dare you!?]

01:35.039 --> 01:37.930
[Episode 2]

01:37.960 --> 01:40.550
[Kunyu Palace]

01:41.350 --> 01:42.210
Your Highness.

01:44.870 --> 01:46.140
Consort Yu sent a message

01:46.140 --> 01:48.560
that she'll come to Kunyu Palace
after noon.

01:48.560 --> 01:49.690
Did she mention why?

01:49.789 --> 01:50.280
No.

01:52.150 --> 01:53.430
In the book, Yu Wanyin

01:53.430 --> 01:55.690
framed others in the harem
and committed all kinds of evil.

01:55.690 --> 01:58.289
Xie Yong'er was completely
under her control.

02:00.040 --> 02:01.310
She was the one behind

02:01.790 --> 02:03.590
my drowning in the pond earlier.

02:05.940 --> 02:08.080
I haven't yet had the chance
to take revenge,

02:08.080 --> 02:11.280
and now this enemy is delivering herself
right to my door.

02:12.000 --> 02:13.810
Since that's the case,

02:21.150 --> 02:22.079
help me find a way

02:22.310 --> 02:24.440
to deliver this sachet to Prince Duan.

02:24.560 --> 02:25.420
And after that,

02:26.000 --> 02:27.520
prepare something for me.

02:42.400 --> 02:44.530
No wonder the flowers here grow better

02:44.750 --> 02:47.280
than other places
in this imperial palace, Yong'er.

02:47.280 --> 02:48.880
So you tend to them yourself.

02:51.190 --> 02:52.590
Lady Yu, how kind of you to come visit.

02:52.590 --> 02:53.790
Please forgive me for

02:54.030 --> 02:55.630
not welcoming you properly.

02:56.150 --> 02:58.130
Why didn't you announce
Consort Yu's arrival?

02:58.130 --> 02:59.560
I saw you were so focused on gardening,

02:59.560 --> 03:00.710
so I didn't want to disturb you.

03:00.710 --> 03:01.640
Don't blame her.

03:03.520 --> 03:06.120
I do enjoy tending to
these flowers and plants,

03:06.430 --> 03:08.360
but it's nothing worthy of notice—

03:08.590 --> 03:09.870
merely a pastime.

03:12.280 --> 03:12.880
Is that so?

03:14.450 --> 03:16.710
We both came here through time traveling.

03:16.710 --> 03:19.040
Why is it that only you speak
with such an affected tone?

03:19.040 --> 03:20.900
This kind of pointless small talk

03:20.960 --> 03:22.840
is really a bit awkward.

03:32.000 --> 03:32.540
Mei,

03:32.750 --> 03:34.560
a new batch of peonies
has just arrived at the flower house.

03:34.560 --> 03:37.000
Let's go get some to display
in the bedchamber.

03:37.000 --> 03:38.430
But my lady...

03:38.800 --> 03:40.130
Don't mind me. Go ahead.

03:45.590 --> 03:48.190
I've just made some osmanthus pastries.

03:48.520 --> 03:49.920
Please try some, Lady Yu.

03:52.710 --> 03:54.510
They're not poisoned, are they?

03:54.650 --> 03:56.079
Logically speaking, the chosen one

03:56.079 --> 03:57.680
wouldn't resort to something so crude.

03:57.680 --> 03:59.180
If her intelligence is really that low,

03:59.180 --> 04:01.980
then she's hardly worth
trying to turn to our side.

04:02.680 --> 04:04.750
These pastries are perfectly crumbly
without falling apart.

04:04.750 --> 04:07.000
Your skills are truly remarkable, Yong'er.

04:07.000 --> 04:08.000
It's just that...

04:09.140 --> 04:10.760
I've been having a toothache lately

04:10.760 --> 04:12.290
and can't eat sweet things.

04:15.800 --> 04:16.600
Then, Lady Yu,

04:17.160 --> 04:18.620
please have some more tea.

04:32.110 --> 04:34.840
It seems she does have
some sophisticated moves.

04:34.870 --> 04:36.510
But if I keep testing her like this,

04:36.510 --> 04:37.970
it will never end, will it?

04:38.560 --> 04:40.159
I'd better turn her quickly.

04:40.920 --> 04:42.310
What brings you here today,

04:42.310 --> 04:43.240
Lady Yu?

04:48.360 --> 04:49.290
My dear Yong'er.

04:49.830 --> 04:51.070
Don't even get me started.

04:51.070 --> 04:52.870
All these titles
like consort and concubine,

04:52.870 --> 04:54.590
they all amount to the same thing
in the end.

04:54.590 --> 04:55.390
If His Majesty

04:56.159 --> 04:58.040
can raise you to the heavens today,

04:58.040 --> 04:59.800
he can cast you into hell tomorrow.

04:59.800 --> 05:01.920
His favor and hatred are nothing
more than a whim.

05:01.920 --> 05:02.430
Lady Yu.

05:02.830 --> 05:03.690
In this palace,

05:04.330 --> 05:06.770
we still have to be careful with
our words.

05:07.510 --> 05:09.710
I trust you won't tell anyone, Yong'er.

05:10.410 --> 05:12.070
In this kind of place, we women

05:12.560 --> 05:15.040
are nothing more than
pawns to be manipulated.

05:15.040 --> 05:17.040
If we don't look out for one another,

05:17.190 --> 05:20.160
wouldn't that just be playing into
those wretched men's hands?

05:20.160 --> 05:21.510
What is she trying to do?

05:21.920 --> 05:23.830
Suddenly cozying up to me for no reason.

05:23.830 --> 05:25.240
Did she get what I meant?

05:25.550 --> 05:27.610
I thought I made myself clear enough.

05:28.190 --> 05:29.040
Girl,

05:29.560 --> 05:30.890
stop being lovestruck.

05:31.270 --> 05:32.270
Forget about men.

05:41.240 --> 05:41.830
I know

05:42.560 --> 05:43.820
it's lonely at the top.

05:44.120 --> 05:45.720
I understand that you were just
feeling sentimental

05:45.720 --> 05:46.950
for a moment, Lady Yu.

05:47.510 --> 05:48.710
What you said just now

05:48.830 --> 05:50.090
doesn't really count.

05:50.310 --> 05:51.570
How could it not count?

05:53.580 --> 05:55.510
I've also made some red bean pastries.

05:55.510 --> 05:56.640
I'll go get them now.

05:57.159 --> 05:59.290
But I haven't finished talking yet...

06:04.190 --> 06:05.790
All that effort for nothing.

06:10.160 --> 06:12.600
She really is just a mindless
2D character.

06:15.520 --> 06:18.380
She'll never break out of
her programmed settings.

06:20.010 --> 06:23.100
Suddenly cozying up to me for no reason—

06:24.810 --> 06:25.740
it's nothing but

06:26.480 --> 06:30.280
an attempt to lull potential enemies
into a false sense of security.

06:34.680 --> 06:37.080
Fortunately, I've read the original work.

06:38.230 --> 06:38.830
My Lady.

06:40.720 --> 06:42.650
This is Prince Duan's return gift.

06:44.770 --> 06:45.940
A lover's lock?

07:01.800 --> 07:03.200
Making such big promises

07:04.560 --> 07:05.890
and failing to deliver.

07:07.800 --> 07:08.860
How embarrassing.

07:10.510 --> 07:11.370
Your Highness!

07:12.160 --> 07:13.160
Your Highness!

07:14.120 --> 07:15.120
What's happening?

07:15.120 --> 07:16.780
Please don't, Your Highness!

07:18.870 --> 07:19.930
What's happening?

07:21.480 --> 07:22.340
Your Highness!

07:22.830 --> 07:24.120
I know I was wrong!

07:24.800 --> 07:26.100
-Please spare me!
-Hurry!

07:26.100 --> 07:27.760
-Please spare me!
-Grab this!

07:28.240 --> 07:28.840
Grab this!

07:37.040 --> 07:37.900
Your Highness!

07:38.640 --> 07:40.360
Your Highness, please spare my life!

07:40.360 --> 07:42.040
I won't dare do it again!

07:42.190 --> 07:43.000
Please have mercy, Your Highness!

07:43.000 --> 07:44.530
What's all this commotion?

07:46.110 --> 07:46.620
Your Majesty.

07:46.620 --> 07:48.320
[Bilan Pavilion]

07:46.950 --> 07:47.430
I

07:47.600 --> 07:48.720
have something to report.

07:48.720 --> 07:49.720
How dare you!

07:50.170 --> 07:52.610
I happened to see Consort Yu

07:53.070 --> 07:54.200
with a man, doing...

07:55.330 --> 07:57.790
Judging by his build,
he seemed to be a guard.

07:57.909 --> 07:59.710
After I caught them, he ran away.

08:01.000 --> 08:02.930
I merely asked Consort Yu about it,

08:03.190 --> 08:04.990
and she pushed me into the water.

08:06.430 --> 08:07.690
I was nowhere near you!

08:08.410 --> 08:10.240
This frame-up is way too obvious.

08:10.240 --> 08:13.560
I beg Your Majesty to grant me justice!

08:15.920 --> 08:17.600
Is that so?

08:20.120 --> 08:21.000
Take away.

08:21.680 --> 08:22.190
Beat.

08:24.800 --> 08:25.600
Your Majesty,

08:25.800 --> 08:27.130
who should we take away?

08:32.039 --> 08:33.000
Why me?

08:33.090 --> 08:34.419
You falsely accused me.

08:34.789 --> 08:35.669
May I ask Your Highness,

08:35.669 --> 08:37.480
have you been to the Peony Garden today?

08:37.480 --> 08:38.280
No, I haven't.

08:38.440 --> 08:42.370
Then why is there Wei Zi peony stain
on the hem of Your Highness's dress?

08:43.150 --> 08:44.550
Throughout the entire palace,

08:44.550 --> 08:46.030
the only place with Wei Zi peonies
is the secluded southwest corner

08:46.030 --> 08:47.160
of the Peony Garden.

08:47.270 --> 08:48.550
If Your Highness hasn't been there,

08:48.550 --> 08:49.880
how did you get stained?

08:52.550 --> 08:53.350
Take him away!

08:54.150 --> 08:55.150
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

08:55.150 --> 08:56.700
Your Majesty, I have a witness!

08:55.300 --> 08:56.620
[Bilan Pavilion]

08:56.960 --> 08:57.390
Where?

08:57.820 --> 08:59.540
[Bilan Pavilion]

08:58.550 --> 08:59.480
Your Majesty...

08:59.660 --> 09:01.510
Take them both away and beat them!

09:01.510 --> 09:02.200
Your Majesty!

09:02.200 --> 09:04.510
I'm telling the truth, Your Majesty!

09:04.790 --> 09:07.440
Your Majesty, I'm innocent!

09:07.960 --> 09:11.390
Your Majesty, please spare my life!

09:12.270 --> 09:12.720
What?

09:13.200 --> 09:15.270
His Majesty actually believed her
so easily?

09:15.270 --> 09:15.670
Yes.

09:16.150 --> 09:18.200
I watched the whole thing
from behind the rockery.

09:18.200 --> 09:20.240
His Majesty didn't even
question that witnesses.

09:20.240 --> 09:21.900
He just had them dragged away.

09:21.910 --> 09:23.510
She didn't mention me at all?

09:23.970 --> 09:24.480
No.

09:25.200 --> 09:27.200
And her answers were very affected.

09:27.240 --> 09:29.120
Who do you think was trying to frame you?

09:29.120 --> 09:30.630
Do you have any suspicions, my dear?

09:30.630 --> 09:32.080
I have no idea, Your Majesty.

09:32.080 --> 09:33.410
You really have no idea?

09:35.790 --> 09:37.720
Your Majesty has so many affairs of state
to attend to every day.

09:37.720 --> 09:40.080
You needn't trouble yourself
with such trivial matters.

09:40.080 --> 09:40.610
Besides,

09:41.280 --> 09:42.060
I have no wish to harm the harmony

09:42.060 --> 09:43.870
among the sisters of the harem.

09:44.550 --> 09:45.410
Whoever it was,

09:46.020 --> 09:47.420
now that the truth is out,

09:48.120 --> 09:50.120
I'm sure she regrets it in her heart.

09:50.480 --> 09:51.280
Your Majesty,

09:51.790 --> 09:53.590
please give her another chance.

09:56.270 --> 09:57.360
Is she too stupid,

09:59.000 --> 10:00.460
or does she lack evidence?

10:01.870 --> 10:03.870
Or is what she said actually true...

10:03.910 --> 10:05.570
In this kind of place, we women

10:06.390 --> 10:08.790
are nothing more than
pawns to be manipulated.

10:08.790 --> 10:10.790
If we don't look out for one another,

10:10.840 --> 10:14.370
wouldn't that just be playing into
those wretched men's hands?

10:15.480 --> 10:15.750
No.

10:16.440 --> 10:17.570
That's impossible.

10:18.150 --> 10:20.030
In the original story,
Yu Wanyin could make all other concubines

10:20.030 --> 10:22.630
become stepping stones
on her path to success.

10:23.080 --> 10:23.870
Her words

10:24.910 --> 10:26.240
can't be trusted at all.

10:26.270 --> 10:30.050
[Yongyan Hall]

10:41.120 --> 10:42.320
Excuse me. Excuse me.

10:55.000 --> 10:55.510
Well,

10:56.910 --> 10:58.370
let me say this in advance—

10:59.550 --> 11:02.080
I've been sleeping here
for several days straight

11:02.080 --> 11:04.240
purely so we can hold strategic meetings

11:04.240 --> 11:06.030
without arousing suspicion.

11:06.390 --> 11:07.550
Yes, sure.

11:08.480 --> 11:11.010
I'm honored you think
so highly of me, Wanyin.

11:14.080 --> 11:15.120
That Xie Yong'er

11:16.630 --> 11:19.290
seems to have really hooked up with
Prince Duan.

11:19.320 --> 11:21.250
So the co-option plan failed, huh?

11:26.790 --> 11:28.870
I was just worried she'd tell Prince Duan.

11:28.870 --> 11:30.840
Otherwise, I would have
confronted her already.

11:30.840 --> 11:32.200
But Xie Yong'er

11:32.910 --> 11:35.840
seems to have built
high emotional walls against me.

11:37.150 --> 11:39.360
Even if I tell her we're both real people,

11:39.360 --> 11:40.760
she might not believe me.

11:40.960 --> 11:42.820
Who says you're both real people?

11:45.000 --> 11:45.480
You are,

11:47.510 --> 11:49.320
but she's just a 2D character
from the book.

11:49.320 --> 11:51.450
Her personality and thought patterns

11:51.550 --> 11:52.750
were predetermined.

11:53.240 --> 11:55.170
If you want her to switch sides now,

11:55.870 --> 11:57.600
it's probably very difficult.

11:59.630 --> 12:00.430
That's right.

12:01.240 --> 12:02.700
How did I not think of that?

12:04.000 --> 12:04.750
Fortunately though,

12:04.750 --> 12:06.960
you're making good progress
turning Xu Yao to our side.

12:06.960 --> 12:07.600
Of course.

12:09.720 --> 12:10.850
Xu Yao is a smart man.

12:11.690 --> 12:13.320
He was just deceived before.

12:13.790 --> 12:15.450
Senior Minister Xu once said,

12:16.360 --> 12:18.360
"the true beneficiary of any matter

12:19.390 --> 12:20.990
is hidden during the process

12:21.780 --> 12:23.690
but revealed in the outcome."

12:24.600 --> 12:27.630
Sometimes by looking through
appearances to the essence,

12:27.630 --> 12:28.480
all mysteries

12:29.650 --> 12:30.870
can be easily solved.

12:33.030 --> 12:34.630
Although those words of mine

12:35.270 --> 12:36.390
might not immediately

12:36.390 --> 12:37.910
turn him to our side,

12:39.210 --> 12:39.960
at least

12:41.120 --> 12:42.630
I've planted a seed

12:43.080 --> 12:44.260
of doubt in his mind.

12:52.120 --> 12:53.320
Xu Yao, oh Xu Yao.

12:54.270 --> 12:55.240
Poor you. Even today,

12:55.240 --> 12:58.500
you still think it was that bastard
who killed your father.

12:58.790 --> 13:00.200
Who foresaw everything

13:00.790 --> 13:02.000
and saved your life?

13:02.750 --> 13:04.610
And who took you in as his watchdog

13:04.960 --> 13:07.020
with a face full of false compassion?

13:15.320 --> 13:16.320
Good, good.

13:16.910 --> 13:18.570
Let's keep going at this pace.

13:19.270 --> 13:22.470
I've been racking my brain these days
trying to remember.

13:23.790 --> 13:25.390
The officials in your court,

13:25.550 --> 13:26.720
70% belong to
the Empress Dowager's faction,

13:26.000 --> 13:27.230
[Empress Dowager's Faction]

13:27.120 --> 13:28.270
and the rest 30% to Prince Duan's faction.

13:27.250 --> 13:32.410
[Prince Duan's Faction]

13:29.080 --> 13:30.240
Empress Dowager is powerful.

13:30.240 --> 13:31.790
Her relatives by marriage
control the court

13:31.790 --> 13:33.320
and have won over most civil officials.

13:32.610 --> 13:34.030
[Civil Officials]

13:34.190 --> 13:39.220
[Military Officials]

13:34.360 --> 13:37.170
The military officials, long oppressed
by the Empress Dowager's faction,

13:37.170 --> 13:39.550
have quietly pledged allegiance
to Prince Duan.

13:39.550 --> 13:41.610
So the most important thing for us now

13:41.710 --> 13:43.510
is to make them fight each other.

13:44.270 --> 13:46.000
We have nothing to lose anyway.

13:46.390 --> 13:47.850
We can sow discord freely.

13:48.200 --> 13:48.790
Ideally,

13:49.550 --> 13:52.240
we'll provoke them into
fighting each other to the death.

13:52.240 --> 13:54.300
Only then can we survive in the chaos.

13:55.750 --> 13:57.880
But as for how exactly to play it out...

13:59.670 --> 14:00.600
I'll improvise.

14:08.630 --> 14:09.190
Oh no.

14:09.350 --> 14:11.280
I suddenly remembered something.

14:22.640 --> 14:24.730
[Drought]

14:24.270 --> 14:24.800
Drought?

14:24.960 --> 14:27.160
The biggest trigger for your overthrow

14:28.360 --> 14:29.510
was a drought.

14:32.720 --> 14:33.360
When?

14:34.390 --> 14:34.990
Next year?

14:35.600 --> 14:36.600
Or the year after?

14:37.950 --> 14:39.790
I-I can't remember clearly.

14:40.750 --> 14:41.630
I think

14:42.750 --> 14:45.120
it was about two-thirds into the book.

14:48.550 --> 14:49.950
When the drought struck,

14:50.720 --> 14:52.380
the national treasury ran dry

14:52.790 --> 14:54.790
and the people were left destitute.

14:54.920 --> 14:56.600
Many across the country starved to death,

14:56.600 --> 14:57.960
chaos spread everywhere—

14:57.960 --> 14:59.390
and then you were assassinated.

14:59.390 --> 15:00.590
Who was the assassin?

15:00.750 --> 15:01.810
When did it happen?

15:02.420 --> 15:03.880
That I actually remember.

15:04.030 --> 15:04.960
It occurred in

15:05.320 --> 15:06.910
the last dozen or so pages of the book.

15:06.910 --> 15:08.440
Can you try to remember
something actually useful?

15:08.440 --> 15:10.900
Something is better than nothing,
isn't it?

15:11.200 --> 15:11.960
Anyway,

15:12.480 --> 15:13.810
after you were stabbed,

15:14.000 --> 15:16.440
Prince Duan entered the palace
claiming to protect you,

15:16.440 --> 15:17.860
but your wounds were fatal,

15:17.860 --> 15:19.520
and the officials petitioned

15:20.000 --> 15:22.730
for him to become emperor
to stabilize the state.

15:24.360 --> 15:26.150
He took the throne in the crisis,

15:26.150 --> 15:27.280
worked diligently,

15:28.310 --> 15:29.550
and eventually became

15:29.550 --> 15:30.720
a great emperor.

15:31.320 --> 15:32.550
Now I see.

15:34.440 --> 15:36.170
When you were reading the book,

15:37.910 --> 15:39.480
you favored Prince Duan.

15:41.670 --> 15:44.670
It's all about perspective.
Perspective determines your position.

15:44.670 --> 15:47.080
We can start searching for
drought-resistant crops now

15:47.080 --> 15:49.880
and find ways to encourage
large-scale planting.

15:50.240 --> 15:51.100
No matter what,

15:51.480 --> 15:53.120
we must address the root cause

15:53.120 --> 15:54.580
to prevent this disaster,

15:55.320 --> 15:57.050
help the people of this country

15:57.240 --> 15:58.240
avoid famine

15:58.960 --> 16:00.760
and safely survive the drought,

16:01.550 --> 16:02.210
and then...

16:02.790 --> 16:04.250
Punch the Empress Dowager

16:04.270 --> 16:05.470
and kick Prince Duan!

16:05.510 --> 16:06.480
You and I

16:07.240 --> 16:08.640
will have the last laugh.

16:10.600 --> 16:12.790
Even if our fate is already
written in the book,

16:12.790 --> 16:14.850
we still have to live it—page by page—

16:16.360 --> 16:18.000
until the end.

16:25.240 --> 16:27.170
General Luo has returned to court!

16:29.030 --> 16:31.360
The Central Army has returned victorious!

16:31.360 --> 16:32.790
Look! The Central Army is back!

16:32.790 --> 16:34.120
General Luo has returned to court!

16:34.120 --> 16:35.720
-The Central Army has returned!
-This is great!

16:35.560 --> 16:38.210
[General Luo]

16:36.550 --> 16:37.810
Long live General Luo!

16:37.920 --> 16:39.280
Long live Great Xia!

16:39.600 --> 16:42.000
The Central Army has returned victorious!

16:43.720 --> 16:44.790
General Luo!

16:46.080 --> 16:47.740
As expected from General Luo.

16:47.840 --> 16:50.600
He drove back the invading Yan forces
a full 300 li.

16:50.100 --> 16:53.240
[Yang Duojie]

16:51.430 --> 16:53.160
Finally, something uplifting

16:53.840 --> 16:55.550
in this turbulent court.

16:56.120 --> 16:56.840
These days,

16:57.090 --> 17:00.240
[Li Yunxi]

16:57.270 --> 16:59.000
only these military officials

16:59.200 --> 17:00.660
are still doing real work.

17:01.000 --> 17:01.960
But I've heard

17:02.360 --> 17:04.160
that Prince Duan once served
as a military officer on the front lines

17:04.160 --> 17:06.109
and fought alongside the soldiers
through life and death,

17:06.109 --> 17:07.829
proving himself quite valiant in battle.

17:07.829 --> 17:09.349
Prince Duan's truly a rare talent

17:09.349 --> 17:11.480
in both strategy and martial prowess.

17:11.720 --> 17:13.440
If he could advance further in court...

17:12.849 --> 17:15.800
[Er Lan]

17:13.790 --> 17:15.270
Too many people, too much gossip.

17:15.270 --> 17:17.349
I advise both of you
to be cautious with your words.

17:17.349 --> 17:18.680
But these are the facts.

17:20.510 --> 17:21.030
Er Lan,

17:22.030 --> 17:23.560
you're being too cautious.

17:29.180 --> 17:32.490
General Luo, you drove the Yan forces back
a full 300 li,

17:33.960 --> 17:36.160
striking fear into all foreign tribes—

17:36.640 --> 17:38.900
truly a display of our Great Xia's might.

17:39.240 --> 17:41.270
I am unworthy of such praise,
Your Majesty.

17:41.270 --> 17:43.130
I've heard that you, General Luo,

17:43.590 --> 17:45.920
have been taking great care of
my brother.

17:49.070 --> 17:49.550
I

17:50.920 --> 17:52.320
was merely doing my duty.

17:53.110 --> 17:54.770
What reward should I give you?

17:58.030 --> 17:59.880
Your Majesty, I have a matter to report.

17:59.880 --> 18:01.450
General Luo came to collect the provisions
the other day,

18:00.370 --> 18:02.660
[Chen Dasui]

18:01.480 --> 18:04.510
but for some reason it was 20% more
than in previous years.

18:04.510 --> 18:06.310
This year's harvest has been poor
across the regions,

18:06.310 --> 18:08.880
and most of the treasury's grain
has gone to disaster relief.

18:08.880 --> 18:11.920
General Luo has suddenly made
such excessive demands,

18:11.920 --> 18:14.440
leaving us rather unprepared.

18:15.790 --> 18:16.590
Your Majesty,

18:16.680 --> 18:18.350
with the same number of troops,

18:18.350 --> 18:21.610
the Central Army has always consumed
the most provisions.

18:21.750 --> 18:24.150
I hope Your Majesty
will judge this fairly.

18:26.750 --> 18:29.410
Brother, you've also once served
at the border.

18:29.480 --> 18:31.080
What's your thought on this?

18:32.150 --> 18:33.880
Since our grain reserves are insufficient

18:33.880 --> 18:35.640
and Your Majesty cares deeply
for the people,

18:35.640 --> 18:36.700
all the main troops

18:36.750 --> 18:38.640
should naturally share
Your Majesty's burden.

18:38.640 --> 18:40.350
Besides, Your Majesty's grace is boundless

18:40.350 --> 18:41.410
and far-reaching.

18:41.720 --> 18:43.670
This matter of
reducing military provisions

18:43.670 --> 18:46.000
is actually for the benefit of
the people.

18:46.550 --> 18:47.200
I believe

18:48.510 --> 18:50.270
each soldier of the Central Army

18:50.270 --> 18:51.310
can understand

18:51.730 --> 18:53.530
Your Majesty's good intentions

18:54.550 --> 18:55.550
and should be able

18:55.880 --> 18:57.480
to show some understanding.

19:10.680 --> 19:12.210
I simply don't understand.

19:12.930 --> 19:15.880
The military provisions have been
the same every year.

19:15.880 --> 19:18.480
Why are they suddenly insufficient
this year?

19:19.200 --> 19:19.960
Is it that

19:20.910 --> 19:23.310
life at the border
has become so comfortable

19:23.310 --> 19:24.200
that everyone

19:24.910 --> 19:25.830
has grown fat?

19:27.540 --> 19:30.750
I'm afraid they've been
lining their own pockets, haven't they?

19:30.750 --> 19:31.550
Your Majesty!

19:32.030 --> 19:33.750
Please allow me to present something

19:33.750 --> 19:34.920
so Your Majesty can see

19:34.920 --> 19:36.800
what our soldiers eat every day.

19:37.270 --> 19:37.930
Bring it in!

19:47.760 --> 19:50.240
These are the provisions
the Ministry of Revenue sent—

19:50.240 --> 19:51.840
half of it is mixed with sand and gravel.

19:51.840 --> 19:53.700
Is this even fit for people to eat?

19:54.310 --> 19:54.920
Nonsense!

19:55.800 --> 19:57.270
Who knows where you got
this brown rice from?

19:57.270 --> 20:00.310
And now you dare to twist the truth
and deceive His Majesty!

20:00.310 --> 20:03.160
His Majesty is discerning.
How could he believe you?

20:03.160 --> 20:05.520
You mixed in sand and gravel yourselves
to deceive His Majesty.

20:05.520 --> 20:07.350
This is a crime of deceiving the emperor!

20:07.350 --> 20:08.720
You all know perfectly well

20:08.720 --> 20:10.110
who mixed in the sand and gravel!

20:10.110 --> 20:11.680
We've been guarding the borders
all year round.

20:11.680 --> 20:13.750
Only you have the leisure
to do such things!

20:13.750 --> 20:15.280
This is complete nonsense!

20:15.720 --> 20:17.240
Then why haven't the other two armies
said anything?

20:15.940 --> 20:17.130
[Grand Tutor Wei]

20:17.240 --> 20:18.170
How would we know

20:18.200 --> 20:19.830
if you've been allocating such provisions

20:19.830 --> 20:20.750
only to the Central Army?

20:20.750 --> 20:21.720
Absurd!

20:22.240 --> 20:23.300
Without evidence,

20:23.440 --> 20:24.960
this is pure slander!

20:25.790 --> 20:26.320
Slander!

20:26.550 --> 20:27.160
Nonsense!

20:28.400 --> 20:29.960
Treating military provisions as a joke

20:29.960 --> 20:32.560
equals treating our soldiers' lives
as a joke!

20:33.000 --> 20:34.750
We risk our lives on the battlefield
year after year!

20:34.750 --> 20:35.440
Enough!

20:38.180 --> 20:39.580
[Cao An]

21:30.110 --> 21:30.640
Your Maj-

21:31.070 --> 21:31.870
Your Majesty!

21:32.000 --> 21:32.460
This...

21:35.270 --> 21:36.070
Your Majesty!

21:36.510 --> 21:39.040
-Your Majesty, what's this for?
-Stop there!

21:40.680 --> 21:41.440
Your Majesty!

21:41.440 --> 21:42.590
W-What is this for?

21:43.250 --> 21:43.850
I am...

21:43.880 --> 21:45.790
I am the Minister of Revenue,
Your Majesty!

21:45.790 --> 21:46.720
I'm Chen Dasui!

21:47.830 --> 21:48.630
Your Majesty!

21:49.510 --> 21:52.170
Can Your Majesty please tell me
what this is for?

21:52.400 --> 21:53.070
Your Majesty!

21:53.070 --> 21:53.400
Hurry...

21:53.350 --> 21:54.550
[Jia Zhong]

21:53.640 --> 21:54.720
Hurry up and stop him!

21:54.720 --> 21:55.720
I said stop there!

21:56.350 --> 21:57.070
Your Majesty!

21:57.070 --> 21:57.830
Your Majesty!

21:57.830 --> 21:59.720
Your Majesty, please don't kill me!
Your Majesty!

21:59.720 --> 22:00.520
Your Majesty!

22:01.350 --> 22:02.150
Your Majesty!

22:05.400 --> 22:06.110
What?

22:07.510 --> 22:09.570
Are you waiting for me to do it myself?

22:25.430 --> 22:27.640
He was laughing too loudly.

22:32.460 --> 22:33.020
You.

22:36.670 --> 22:39.550
Go collect the provisions from
the Ministry of Revenue yourself.

22:39.550 --> 22:40.950
Thank you, Your Majesty.

22:49.520 --> 22:52.970
[Prince Duan's Mansion]

22:51.160 --> 22:53.020
Was His Majesty's outburst today

22:53.550 --> 22:54.810
really a coincidence?

22:55.160 --> 22:58.160
Whether it was a coincidence or not,

22:59.350 --> 23:01.590
with the Minister of Revenue dead,

23:01.880 --> 23:02.790
the Empress Dowager's faction

23:02.790 --> 23:05.270
will surely hold us accountable for this.

23:06.440 --> 23:09.440
His Majesty has always acted
without a clear pattern.

23:09.510 --> 23:12.000
If he's truly gone crazy,
it's hardly surprising.

23:12.000 --> 23:13.200
I'm just worried that

23:13.510 --> 23:17.040
the Empress Dowager may use this
as an excuse to take it out on us.

23:18.510 --> 23:20.310
Even without today's incident,

23:20.350 --> 23:22.160
the Empress Dowager
would still target us at every turn.

23:22.160 --> 23:23.090
At least for now,

23:23.440 --> 23:26.100
the Central Army's soldiers can
eat their fill—

23:26.240 --> 23:28.240
that's something to be happy about.

23:29.170 --> 23:31.170
But if the Central Army's well-fed,

23:32.430 --> 23:34.230
who will still hate His Majesty?

23:34.920 --> 23:35.480
Exactly.

23:36.120 --> 23:38.380
Look at how joyful General Luo was today,

23:38.400 --> 23:39.110
as if he's forgotten

23:38.480 --> 23:41.980
[Wu Jiadong]

23:39.640 --> 23:40.900
who the true culprit is

23:40.980 --> 23:42.590
behind the chaos in the court

23:42.960 --> 23:45.240
caused by the Empress Dowager's faction.

23:45.240 --> 23:47.070
The Central Army fought valiantly,

23:47.070 --> 23:49.000
using their bodies as shields
against enemies,

23:49.000 --> 23:50.530
and just achieved victory.

23:50.880 --> 23:52.350
No matter how fierce
the political struggle,

23:52.350 --> 23:54.680
they shouldn't be made pawns in this game.

23:54.750 --> 23:56.480
Though we've defeated the Yan State
for the time being,

23:56.480 --> 23:58.210
if we dishearten our soldiers,

23:58.910 --> 24:01.570
who will defend against
the Qiang and Shu States

24:02.070 --> 24:03.250
in the future?

24:03.790 --> 24:05.190
Sir, your righteousness

24:06.680 --> 24:07.830
puts me to shame.

24:09.350 --> 24:11.280
Sir, you shouldn't put it that way.

24:11.450 --> 24:13.650
His Highness has already
prepared provisions

24:13.650 --> 24:15.710
to supply the Central Army in secret.

24:16.480 --> 24:19.240
This way, the soldiers can eat their fill

24:19.590 --> 24:22.400
while His Majesty loses authority
in the ranks—

24:23.270 --> 24:25.510
a foolproof plan.

24:25.960 --> 24:28.030
The only flaw was that

24:28.510 --> 24:29.640
no one expected

24:30.070 --> 24:32.350
a mad emperor to throw everything off.

24:32.610 --> 24:34.540
The true beneficiary of any matter

24:34.880 --> 24:36.480
is hidden during the process

24:36.490 --> 24:38.300
but revealed in the outcome.

24:43.490 --> 24:44.350
Your Highness,

24:44.750 --> 24:46.950
I was hasty and disrespectful earlier.

24:47.200 --> 24:48.270
Please forgive me.

24:49.030 --> 24:50.310
No need for that, Sir.

24:51.350 --> 24:53.550
The truth is exactly what I want to hear.

24:53.790 --> 24:55.200
However, just now you didn't

24:55.200 --> 24:57.660
comment on His Majesty's unusual behavior.

24:59.270 --> 25:01.350
Perhaps you could share your thoughts now?

25:01.350 --> 25:02.010
His Majesty

25:03.000 --> 25:05.460
has been acting rather differently lately.

25:05.590 --> 25:06.190
Could it be

25:06.790 --> 25:09.320
he's got some skilled strategist
by his side?

25:11.720 --> 25:14.180
But our palace informants haven't reported

25:15.110 --> 25:18.170
His Majesty being in close contact with
anyone lately.

25:19.750 --> 25:21.110
Someone he's been close to?

25:20.660 --> 25:23.510
[Fan Ke]

25:22.070 --> 25:23.680
I can think of one person.

25:24.030 --> 25:24.650
Who?

25:24.680 --> 25:26.480
The demonic consort, Yu Wanyin.

25:34.510 --> 25:35.240
Villain!

25:35.830 --> 25:37.030
An absolute villain!

25:38.030 --> 25:39.360
No matter what he wears,

25:39.880 --> 25:41.080
he's still a villain!

25:42.030 --> 25:44.180
He not only washed his hands of it
completely,

25:44.180 --> 25:45.110
but even claimed

25:45.510 --> 25:46.240
the soldiers

25:46.830 --> 25:49.160
all appreciated my painstaking concern.

25:49.590 --> 25:50.790
With a single remark,

25:51.440 --> 25:52.550
he both cemented the fact
that the Empress Dowager's faction

25:52.550 --> 25:54.750
had been harsh with the army provisions

25:54.830 --> 25:56.760
and even dragged me into it as well,

25:56.830 --> 25:58.760
as if I had instructed them to do so.

25:59.350 --> 26:00.880
What's more infuriating is

26:01.000 --> 26:02.130
that on the surface,

26:02.270 --> 26:04.130
you can't find any fault with him.

26:05.750 --> 26:06.920
It's truly maddening.

26:06.920 --> 26:09.350
How else could he have turned

26:09.480 --> 26:11.370
a terrible hand into a winning one
in the novel?

26:11.370 --> 26:11.970
That's why

26:12.440 --> 26:14.240
you need to be even more ruthless
than him.

26:14.240 --> 26:15.040
Four of a kind!

26:16.350 --> 26:17.410
I can't match that.

26:18.400 --> 26:19.350
That said,

26:20.070 --> 26:21.440
this stunt of suddenly "losing your mind"

26:21.440 --> 26:23.480
and taking the Minister of Revenue
out of the picture

26:23.480 --> 26:24.810
wasn't exactly clever.

26:24.830 --> 26:26.510
Aren't you worried
they'll set their sights on you?

26:26.510 --> 26:28.030
What's there to worry about?

26:28.030 --> 26:29.890
I'm the "mad emperor," after all—

26:29.920 --> 26:31.800
small fits every 3 days,
big ones every 5.

26:31.800 --> 26:34.240
If I weren't acting crazy,
that would be strange.

26:34.240 --> 26:34.770
Besides,

26:35.550 --> 26:36.830
Prince Duan and the Empress Dowager

26:36.830 --> 26:38.880
are busy planning their next move
right now.

26:38.880 --> 26:39.960
They have no time to care about me,

26:39.960 --> 26:41.560
a powerless puppet emperor.

26:42.160 --> 26:42.890
That's true.

26:44.240 --> 26:45.200
Three.

26:45.640 --> 26:46.970
I'll follow with a four.

26:47.750 --> 26:49.510
Xu Yao should be

26:49.530 --> 26:51.990
investigating that incident by now, right?

26:52.110 --> 26:52.970
It's just a pity

26:53.480 --> 26:56.160
there seems to be no evidence
against Prince Duan.

26:56.160 --> 26:57.510
Evidence is something

26:57.920 --> 26:59.270
that can be fabricated.

27:03.270 --> 27:06.670
Didn't you already send people
to pick up Senior Minister Xu?

27:06.680 --> 27:07.790
On the way back,

27:08.480 --> 27:10.480
deliberately create a few slip-ups

27:10.480 --> 27:11.540
to make him believe

27:11.880 --> 27:13.740
the information has been leaked.

27:14.750 --> 27:15.750
Then send someone

27:17.000 --> 27:18.460
to assassinate his father

27:19.640 --> 27:21.960
and frame Prince Duan for it.

27:23.550 --> 27:24.950
After that, your people,

27:25.350 --> 27:26.590
against all odds,

27:27.000 --> 27:29.400
save him from certain death.

27:30.110 --> 27:32.510
Xu Yao will be overwhelmed with gratitude.

27:32.750 --> 27:33.720
And from then on,

27:34.590 --> 27:36.350
he'll be at our disposal.

27:44.480 --> 27:46.070
If only it could go that smoothly.

27:46.070 --> 27:47.400
Just thinking out loud.

27:47.680 --> 27:49.880
Can't we have a little fun fantasizing?

27:52.440 --> 27:54.170
Let's take it one step at a time.

27:54.680 --> 27:55.960
Didn't we talk about

27:56.510 --> 27:58.000
preventing the drought before?

27:58.000 --> 27:59.270
I want to go to the library

27:59.270 --> 28:01.110
and look up materials on
drought-resistant crops.

28:01.110 --> 28:01.770
Go on ahead.

28:02.640 --> 28:04.200
The library has quite a collection.

28:04.200 --> 28:06.000
Those materials won't be easy to find.

28:06.000 --> 28:06.640
I won!

28:08.200 --> 28:09.510
It's just looking up some information.

28:09.510 --> 28:10.030
Don't underestimate

28:10.030 --> 28:13.030
the abilities of
a seasoned corporate drudge like me.

28:35.480 --> 28:38.280
These traditional characters
are so hard to read.

28:40.000 --> 28:41.720
The calligraphy conventions
in ancient times

28:41.720 --> 28:44.180
are completely different from modern ones.

28:47.550 --> 28:49.080
Your Highness Prince Duan.

28:52.480 --> 28:53.340
Your Highness.

28:55.490 --> 28:56.380
Why is he here?

29:05.070 --> 29:05.550
Mr. Xu.

29:05.960 --> 29:06.880
Mr. Xu?

29:07.310 --> 29:08.270
Let's split up to search.

29:08.270 --> 29:08.880
Xu Yao?

29:08.920 --> 29:09.270
Okay.

29:12.310 --> 29:13.510
I can't be certain yet

29:13.880 --> 29:16.160
if this Prince Duan here
is the original character.

29:16.160 --> 29:17.030
To be safe,

29:17.550 --> 29:19.350
I should recall the original text.

29:19.350 --> 29:20.550
The original text...

29:26.750 --> 29:27.350
Oh, right.

29:28.030 --> 29:29.750
Before Yu Wanyin entered the palace,

29:29.750 --> 29:31.350
she had met Prince Duan once.

29:31.880 --> 29:33.790
Yu Wanyin fell in love at first sight

29:33.790 --> 29:35.990
and pined for him after returning home.

29:36.240 --> 29:38.830
Later, Yu Wanyin was forced by her family
to enter the palace with resentment,

29:38.830 --> 29:41.360
resulting in an unrequited love
throughout.

29:41.510 --> 29:42.950
So it was kind of like a secret crush.

29:42.950 --> 29:44.680
Secret crush, secret crush...

29:53.830 --> 29:54.490
Where is he?

29:55.600 --> 29:57.060
Your Highness Consort Yu?

30:04.280 --> 30:05.810
Your Highness Prince Duan?

30:07.800 --> 30:09.600
What brings Your Highness here?

30:10.070 --> 30:11.530
I wanted to look for a book,

30:12.010 --> 30:13.740
but I couldn't find it just now.

30:14.350 --> 30:16.160
I might have remembered it wrong.

30:16.160 --> 30:17.220
Still pretending.

30:17.350 --> 30:18.680
Go on, keep pretending.

30:19.210 --> 30:19.760
Well,

30:20.750 --> 30:22.510
what book is Your Highness looking for?

30:22.510 --> 30:24.040
I can help you search for it.

30:24.440 --> 30:26.300
I'll trouble Your Highness then.

30:26.480 --> 30:27.480
The book is called

30:28.240 --> 30:30.100
"Classic of Mountains and Seas."

30:30.160 --> 30:32.270
It contains many rare
and strange creatures,

30:32.270 --> 30:33.000
one of which

30:34.110 --> 30:35.170
is called Zhulong.

30:36.140 --> 30:38.800
It can freely travel
between different worlds.

30:40.510 --> 30:41.920
I am quite curious

30:42.680 --> 30:44.140
and want to find it to read.

30:44.310 --> 30:46.240
What "Classic of Mountains and Seas"?

30:46.240 --> 30:47.160
All that talk

30:48.030 --> 30:49.690
was just to test me, wasn't it?

30:51.000 --> 30:53.000
At the palace banquet a few days ago,

30:54.690 --> 30:57.420
Your Highness was also lost in thought
like this.

30:58.960 --> 31:00.000
It seemed you had

31:00.880 --> 31:02.410
a lot of doubts on your mind.

31:04.910 --> 31:06.510
I wouldn't call them doubts.

31:07.920 --> 31:09.120
I just never expected

31:10.240 --> 31:13.070
that the gentleman I met
at the Lantern Festival market

31:13.070 --> 31:15.550
would turn out to be
the renowned Prince Duan.

31:15.550 --> 31:17.480
I was on official business that day

31:17.510 --> 31:19.370
and couldn't reveal my identity.

31:19.880 --> 31:21.590
I hope Your Highness wouldn't mind.

31:21.590 --> 31:22.480
I understand.

31:23.240 --> 31:25.160
We were both out incognito that day.

31:25.160 --> 31:27.490
Of course we couldn't make
a big show of it.

31:31.590 --> 31:33.700
The details of our first meeting
all line up now, right?

31:33.700 --> 31:37.610
[Round 1]
[1:0]

31:37.310 --> 31:39.910
I've been cut off from news
while in the palace.

31:39.920 --> 31:42.240
I wonder whether things are well
at home.

31:44.030 --> 31:46.290
I actually saw your father a few days ago.

31:46.480 --> 31:47.200
Minister Yu

31:48.000 --> 31:49.330
is in excellent health.

31:51.200 --> 31:53.200
He's even taken up the tea ceremony.

31:53.400 --> 31:54.200
Tea ceremony?

31:55.270 --> 31:57.000
My father in the original story

31:57.030 --> 31:58.560
wasn't this refined at all.

31:59.680 --> 32:00.030
Also,

32:00.440 --> 32:02.240
he's learned to play card games.

32:03.070 --> 32:03.920
But I heard

32:04.640 --> 32:05.500
his luck is poor

32:06.270 --> 32:07.670
and he's lost quite a bit.

32:09.480 --> 32:10.830
Well, gambling harms the body,

32:10.830 --> 32:12.960
while drinking tea dispels excess heat.

32:12.960 --> 32:14.110
I was almost scared to death.

32:14.110 --> 32:15.260
I thought I remembered it wrong.

32:15.180 --> 32:18.270
[Round 2]
[2:0]

32:18.480 --> 32:20.410
Your Highness was very shy before.

32:21.790 --> 32:23.320
What exactly happened that

32:24.070 --> 32:25.240
in just a few months,

32:25.920 --> 32:27.520
you've become so talkative?

32:29.790 --> 32:31.320
I've always been like this.

32:32.110 --> 32:33.160
It's just that

32:33.790 --> 32:36.510
I'd never had a deep conversation
with Your Highness before.

32:36.510 --> 32:39.370
But it's not just your temperament
that's changed—

32:39.720 --> 32:40.960
even the way you dress

32:41.590 --> 32:43.250
is completely different now.

32:43.750 --> 32:44.440
It's as if

32:46.590 --> 32:48.520
you've become a different person.

32:53.510 --> 32:54.550
There's a flaw.

32:57.350 --> 32:59.030
Who could remain unchanged

32:59.480 --> 33:01.810
after entering this locked-away palace?

33:02.070 --> 33:04.930
After all, with thousands of beauties
in the harem,

33:05.000 --> 33:06.440
I still want to survive.

33:09.030 --> 33:12.350
Your Highness, please don't mention
these words to others.

33:12.350 --> 33:14.030
I'll pretend I never heard them.

33:14.030 --> 33:15.880
As expected, at crucial moments,

33:15.880 --> 33:17.680
playing the victim still works.

33:17.810 --> 33:21.670
[Round 3]
[3:0]

33:22.750 --> 33:24.480
So Your Highness was painting?

33:27.850 --> 33:29.780
Your Highness, please don't look.

33:30.910 --> 33:31.500
This is bad...

33:31.400 --> 33:33.630
[Round 4]

33:33.940 --> 33:36.920
[Hungry… all I see is braised pork belly
colorful and dazzling hehe dipping shrimp]

33:35.110 --> 33:35.990
This painting

33:36.480 --> 33:38.720
looks charmingly childlike.

33:39.960 --> 33:41.000
I like it a lot.

33:41.510 --> 33:43.310
It's just some random scribbles

33:43.430 --> 33:45.160
not worthy of being displayed.

33:45.790 --> 33:47.030
Might Your Highness be willing to

33:47.030 --> 33:49.160
bestow this painting of yours upon me?

33:54.880 --> 33:56.610
If Your Highness doesn't mind,

33:56.920 --> 33:58.050
feel free to take it.

34:05.310 --> 34:06.170
Your Highness,

34:06.750 --> 34:07.880
I've found the book.

34:08.880 --> 34:09.409
Alright.

34:16.510 --> 34:18.000
Then thank you, Your Highness.

34:18.000 --> 34:20.860
I will certainly bring a gift
in return another day.

34:22.000 --> 34:22.860
I take my leave.

34:27.760 --> 34:28.820
Wasn't this sachet

34:29.320 --> 34:29.960
the token

34:29.960 --> 34:32.219
he and Xie Yong'er exchanged
in the book?

34:34.190 --> 34:37.190
Seems like they've already
hooked up with each other.

34:37.840 --> 34:39.230
Have you discovered anything?

34:39.230 --> 34:40.560
Just from this meeting,

34:40.760 --> 34:42.560
I couldn't detect any scheming.

34:42.590 --> 34:43.120
However,

34:43.880 --> 34:45.679
her eyes are cunning and shrewd,

34:45.960 --> 34:47.920
suggesting she has many thoughts
hidden away.

34:47.920 --> 34:50.480
No wonder she managed to
win His Majesty's favor.

34:50.480 --> 34:52.010
Was there anything strange

34:52.320 --> 34:53.850
about her words or actions?

34:55.920 --> 34:56.710
Strange...

34:59.000 --> 35:00.800
What do you mean, Your Highness?

35:04.490 --> 35:09.210
[Hungry… rustic style…  braised pork ribs,
colorful, white, yellow and black]

35:04.590 --> 35:05.440
Go and check

35:06.000 --> 35:07.590
if she left behind
any calligraphy or paintings

35:07.590 --> 35:09.190
before entering the palace.

35:09.600 --> 35:12.130
The answer might be found
at the Yu Residence.

35:24.760 --> 35:27.690
Consort Yu is still compiling books
so late at night?

35:29.030 --> 35:31.630
She must want to share
Your Majesty's burdens.

35:32.000 --> 35:33.200
This kind of devotion

35:34.110 --> 35:35.150
is so touching

35:35.880 --> 35:37.280
that even I'm moved.

35:51.070 --> 35:52.870
Have you worked yourself up yet?

35:54.030 --> 35:56.360
Don't force it if there are no tears,
okay?

36:02.800 --> 36:04.320
Later, have the Imperial Kitchen

36:04.320 --> 36:05.780
bring her some nourishing

36:05.840 --> 36:07.510
and easily digestible late-night snacks.

36:07.510 --> 36:08.570
Yes, Your Majesty.

36:31.920 --> 36:32.440
Yu...

36:44.070 --> 36:45.550
I'm about to be late!

36:46.150 --> 36:47.400
Why didn't I know about this?

36:47.400 --> 36:48.760
Do we have to go pay respects every day?

36:48.760 --> 36:50.400
Originally it was
every morning and evening,

36:50.400 --> 36:51.540
but the Empress Dowager
prefers peace and quiet,

36:51.540 --> 36:53.080
so the date of respect paying
was changed to

36:53.080 --> 36:54.230
only the 1st and 15th of each month.

36:54.230 --> 36:55.690
So everyone will be there?

36:55.920 --> 36:56.440
My Lady.

36:57.400 --> 36:58.550
This is bad. This is bad!

36:58.550 --> 36:59.030
My Lady!

36:59.360 --> 37:00.820
My Lady, please slow down!

37:02.510 --> 37:02.970
Sister,

37:03.710 --> 37:05.310
do you think it looks pretty?

37:06.840 --> 37:07.510
It does.

37:08.840 --> 37:09.970
It's really pretty.

37:10.590 --> 37:12.590
Grand Tutor Wei truly cares for you,

37:12.590 --> 37:14.510
finding such rare red agate

37:14.800 --> 37:16.600
as your birthday gift, Lady Wei.

37:17.880 --> 37:18.960
In comparison,

37:19.760 --> 37:21.420
the gifts we sisters prepared

37:21.760 --> 37:23.630
seem almost embarrassing to give.

37:23.630 --> 37:24.960
Don't say that, Sister.

37:25.480 --> 37:27.630
Gifts are about the thoughts behind them,

37:27.630 --> 37:28.560
not their value.

37:30.030 --> 37:31.760
About what happened
at the palace banquet last time,

37:31.760 --> 37:33.220
I haven't thanked you yet.

37:33.800 --> 37:35.330
No need to thank me, Sister.

37:36.190 --> 37:37.230
I did it

37:38.710 --> 37:41.030
mainly to stand up for you, Sister.

37:42.280 --> 37:42.840
Why?

37:43.320 --> 37:44.550
Why else could it be?

37:45.280 --> 37:47.440
Sister, you have the looks,
the family background,

37:47.440 --> 37:48.770
and a good temperament,

37:49.230 --> 37:51.360
yet His Majesty doesn't see it.

37:52.510 --> 37:53.320
Instead, he favors

37:53.320 --> 37:54.280
-that improper Yu...
-Enough.

37:54.280 --> 37:55.320
Stop it.

37:56.000 --> 37:57.960
Now that she has His Majesty's favor,

37:57.960 --> 38:00.000
she doesn't even bother coming to
pay respects to the Empress Dowager.

38:00.000 --> 38:02.150
How could she possibly
care about us sisters?

38:02.150 --> 38:02.920
Exactly.

38:03.320 --> 38:04.510
We can let it slide,

38:04.800 --> 38:06.590
but you're different, Lady Wei.

38:06.590 --> 38:09.360
Your father is Grand Tutor Wei,
backed by the Empress Dowager.

38:09.360 --> 38:11.880
How could you let yourself
be overshadowed by her?

38:11.880 --> 38:13.740
So what if His Majesty favors her?

38:13.920 --> 38:14.920
When she arrives,

38:15.480 --> 38:19.080
I will discipline her properly
on behalf of the Empress Dowager.

38:35.480 --> 38:37.510
Concubine Yu, you're so late.

38:38.360 --> 38:40.880
Have you forgotten all the rules
you learned when entering the palace?

38:40.880 --> 38:41.540
Sister Wei.

38:42.150 --> 38:44.750
Concubine Yu has been promoted
to Consort now.

38:46.800 --> 38:47.670
No wonder.

38:48.590 --> 38:49.650
Such poor manners.

38:50.590 --> 38:52.450
Again with this tasteless trick.

38:53.320 --> 38:54.190
What a headache.

38:54.190 --> 38:55.710
Hold it in. Stay calm.

38:58.360 --> 38:59.360
I took a wrong turn

38:59.550 --> 39:00.610
and lost some time.

39:00.760 --> 39:02.490
Please don't blame me, Sister.

39:04.550 --> 39:05.630
What's with that look?

39:05.630 --> 39:06.910
Did you just roll your eyes at me?

39:06.910 --> 39:08.150
Did she just roll her eyes at me?

39:08.150 --> 39:09.960
She did, she definitely did.

39:09.960 --> 39:11.150
I saw it. I saw it.

39:11.150 --> 39:11.880
I didn't.

39:11.920 --> 39:13.250
Yu Wanyin, how dare you!

39:21.920 --> 39:23.590
I naturally have a scowling face

39:23.590 --> 39:24.710
and occasional eye twitches.

39:24.710 --> 39:26.280
It's not aimed at anyone in particular.

39:26.280 --> 39:28.280
I hope you can understand, Sisters.

39:28.670 --> 39:29.070
You...

39:30.030 --> 39:30.690
Sister Wei.

39:31.630 --> 39:33.290
Sister Wei, please calm down.

39:33.920 --> 39:34.850
Consort Yu might

39:35.010 --> 39:37.360
really have been busy with
important matters

39:37.360 --> 39:38.670
and got held up.

39:41.400 --> 39:42.650
What could be more important

39:42.650 --> 39:45.000
than paying respects
to the Empress Dowager?

39:45.000 --> 39:46.150
I know.

39:46.670 --> 39:48.800
I bet she went to the Imperial Garden

39:49.190 --> 39:51.670
to meet secretly with some guard again.

39:52.630 --> 39:53.380
Sister.

39:53.590 --> 39:55.590
You'd better not speak recklessly.

39:55.800 --> 39:57.860
She might go cry to His Majesty again,

39:57.960 --> 39:59.840
and then...

39:59.840 --> 40:00.660
Then what?

40:02.820 --> 40:04.550
Greetings, Your Majesty.

40:05.480 --> 40:07.340
Why are you kneeling too, my dear?

40:07.410 --> 40:10.210
I permit you not to kneel
when you see me from now on.

40:10.550 --> 40:10.880
Here.

40:14.240 --> 40:16.100
Be careful not to hurt your knees.

40:16.940 --> 40:18.340
Thank you, Your Majesty.

40:21.850 --> 40:22.780
Why are you here?

40:23.400 --> 40:24.330
If I hadn't come,

40:24.660 --> 40:26.550
they would have bullied you to death.

40:26.550 --> 40:28.010
They weren't bullying me.

40:28.070 --> 40:29.600
We were just joking around.

40:33.190 --> 40:33.920
Just now,

40:35.710 --> 40:37.310
who among you was gossiping?

40:42.670 --> 40:43.070
You?

40:46.040 --> 40:46.800
Me?

40:47.590 --> 40:48.850
Tell me what happened.

40:49.110 --> 40:50.840
I admit my guilt, Your Majesty!

40:51.920 --> 40:52.670
Very well,

40:52.920 --> 40:53.850
that saves time.

40:54.710 --> 40:55.510
Take her away!

40:55.620 --> 40:56.150
Your Majesty!

40:56.150 --> 40:56.630
Throw her into the Cold Palace!

40:56.630 --> 40:57.840
I admit my guilt, Your Majesty!

40:57.840 --> 40:58.510
No, please!

40:58.800 --> 40:59.800
I admit my guilt!

41:00.000 --> 41:00.800
Your Majesty!

41:00.960 --> 41:01.510
Your Majesty!

41:01.510 --> 41:01.840
You.

41:02.840 --> 41:03.900
Explain yourself.

41:07.710 --> 41:08.060
I...

41:08.280 --> 41:10.230
I only wanted to remind Consort Yu

41:10.480 --> 41:11.940
to follow the palace rules

41:12.000 --> 41:14.150
and serve the Empress Dowager
and Your Majesty properly.

41:14.150 --> 41:14.950
Take her away!

41:15.240 --> 41:16.670
Your Majesty, please let me explain.

41:16.670 --> 41:17.200
I just...

41:17.670 --> 41:18.070
You...

41:18.230 --> 41:19.960
-She really just gossiped for a bit.
-Your Majesty!

41:19.960 --> 41:20.710
There's no need for that.

41:20.710 --> 41:21.770
Noble Consort Wei.

41:22.760 --> 41:23.820
Explain yourself.

41:24.150 --> 41:24.950
Your Majesty!

41:26.020 --> 41:27.400
-It's really not that serious.
-I beg Your Majesty,

41:27.400 --> 41:30.000
in light of my father's devoted service
to you,

41:30.400 --> 41:32.000
to spare me. Please spare me.

41:32.030 --> 41:34.280
I know your father is Grand Tutor Wei.

41:34.710 --> 41:35.440
So what?

41:37.440 --> 41:38.240
Take her away!

41:38.590 --> 41:40.370
Your Majesty, I admit my guilt!

41:40.400 --> 41:43.280
My son, what a show of power.

41:43.300 --> 41:44.160
Here she comes,

41:45.110 --> 41:46.960
one of the main villains of the story,

41:46.960 --> 41:48.960
who's also Xiahou Dan's stepmother,

41:48.960 --> 41:50.160
the Empress Dowager.

41:51.230 --> 41:52.890
This proud and arrogant woman

41:53.070 --> 41:54.400
is obsessed with power.

41:54.920 --> 41:56.670
Ever since Xiahou Dan started disobeying,

41:56.670 --> 41:58.510
she resorted to some underhanded methods

41:58.510 --> 42:00.320
to make him father a young crown prince,

42:00.320 --> 42:02.050
keeping him close as a new pawn.

42:02.320 --> 42:03.120
That's right.

42:03.230 --> 42:04.360
This is Xiahou Dan's

42:05.320 --> 42:06.150
own son.

42:08.800 --> 42:09.290
Mother.

42:10.360 --> 42:11.820
Greetings, Your Majesty.

42:11.960 --> 42:12.880
Greetings, Father.

42:12.420 --> 42:14.380
[Crown Prince]

42:16.270 --> 42:18.590
[Empress Dowager]

42:19.960 --> 42:20.800
Rise.

42:21.840 --> 42:23.240
Thank you, Your Majesty.

42:30.150 --> 42:31.360
My son.

42:32.230 --> 42:35.440
Not only have you been wreaking havoc
in the court,

42:36.150 --> 42:38.280
but today in my presence,

42:38.590 --> 42:40.850
you're also showing off your authority?

42:41.320 --> 42:43.070
Mother, you've learned about

42:43.670 --> 42:44.920
what happened in the court so quickly.

42:44.920 --> 42:46.520
I'd rather not have learned.

42:47.760 --> 42:49.620
But look at you, acting so crazed.

42:49.840 --> 42:51.500
The whole palace knows by now.

42:51.510 --> 42:52.910
How could I not hear of it?

42:56.190 --> 42:58.790
They gave me such a headache
with their clamor.

42:59.590 --> 43:00.990
Don't they deserve to die?

43:00.990 --> 43:02.280
You wanted to kill them

43:02.840 --> 43:04.570
just because they annoyed you?

43:04.710 --> 43:05.310
What else?

43:05.760 --> 43:06.670
So you mean

43:08.180 --> 43:09.520
it was all their fault?

43:09.550 --> 43:10.360
Indeed.

43:11.670 --> 43:13.000
Well, that makes sense.

43:13.190 --> 43:15.880
How could the Emperor possibly be wrong?

43:17.190 --> 43:18.280
If there's blame,

43:19.360 --> 43:21.280
it must lie with someone else.

43:22.470 --> 43:23.670
Impudent Consort Yu!

43:23.960 --> 43:25.440
Bewitching the Emperor
and deceiving his judgment—

43:25.440 --> 43:26.500
you deserve death!

43:26.550 --> 43:27.000
Guards!

43:27.000 --> 43:27.320
Yes!

43:27.800 --> 43:30.070
Seize this demon consort
who has thrown the court into chaos

43:30.070 --> 43:32.400
and shows no respect for her elders,

43:32.800 --> 43:34.510
and drag her away to be buried alive!

43:34.510 --> 43:35.640
I dare anyone to try!

43:38.190 --> 43:38.920
How dare you!

43:39.110 --> 43:41.110
You don't rule this palace yet!

43:41.550 --> 43:42.320
Seize her now!

43:42.320 --> 43:42.760
Mother!
